{"tid":113159,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國傳奇集團擬收購TVB 電視廣播：對買方未有所聞","createTime":"2017-02-08T16:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T04:43:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a83f14d5a861ef7324b4171f16c6958c8d71d4c","tid":113159,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170208/large/1486556356_92d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170208%2Flarge%2F1486556356_92d5.jpg&h=a5db5851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【新增TVB回應】<br />\n<br />\n電視廣播(TVB、511)發通告指，收到傳奇影業及娛樂集團於昨日向TVB發出一份函件，知會董事會就收購TVB 29.9%已發行股份進行正式討論。如果落實，會成為TVB單一最大股東。TVB發通告指，對可能買方未有所聞，亦未獲披露可能買方的最終實益擁有人身份、其資金來源及其財務穩健的證明。<br />\nTVB昨日中午突然宣佈停牌，停牌前收報29.65元，跌0.8%，公司將於明日復牌。<br />\n通告中提到，建議要先達成兩項條件，第一是TVB上月底的回購計劃要遭股東投票否決。第二是收購要獲得通訊事務管理局批准或不遭其反對。<br />\n據通告顯示，傳奇影業及娛樂集團股東為衛浩材及童煒晉，二人分別為傳奇集團（香港）控股的非執行董事及董事，公司從事文化產業及房地產開發及投資業務。<br />\n據傳奇集團(香港)控股網頁介紹，公司專門致力於文化產業投資及相關的地產項目開發，總部位於北京，在香港和上海設有分部。傳奇集團旗下有四家子公司，分別從事全球影視媒體投資，文化地產投資，以及文化產業類企業的股權併購和整合。<br />\n現時大股東陳國強、宏達電（HTC）創辦人及董事長王雪紅及有「中國梅鐸」之稱的黎瑞剛持有的Young Lion持有TVB 26%股權，計同「六嬸」方逸華持有的3.9%，上述人士合共持有TVB29.9%股權。<br />\nTVB上月底提出建議回購最多1.38億股，每股作價30.5元，涉及已發行股本約31.51%，涉及資金42.09億元。倘若建議回購計劃全額完成，已發行股本將由4.38億股，下降至3億股，黎瑞剛及方逸華等一致行動人士於TVB的持股權將29.9%增至43.66%。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170208/56278774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170208%2F56278774&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=22ace123\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170208%2F56278774&h=1a1924cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170208/56278774</a>"},{"pid":"ec09c9f55b99b61723362d1a18a7c75f708d3034","tid":113159,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:10:19.000Z","msg":"WFC"},{"pid":"5b0bfc42609cbda609afe07cbe1c7e8aa5e8297e","tid":113159,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:32:42.000Z","msg":"會勁拍抗日神劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657db0fef184f330a5a67bb0f9b54f83f6147577","tid":113159,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:43:49.000Z","msg":"亞視永恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30edb9cf81855d09ef8498a1ddc65058a8bfa72","tid":113159,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T18:03:21.000Z","msg":"係咪又係習派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb83a1b10ac35ce39eab2b8cb079fc616fef1865","tid":113159,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:07:25.000Z","msg":"邵逸夫開始冇理已經走下坡<br />\n易左手之後更加係戇鳩"},{"pid":"c2983ea2ca0b3f4eeab30ab222b0f0da60990879","tid":113159,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbaedb66335fdb92de9efcd2ad8a68cbf9d0f41b","tid":113159,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:14:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9af49411abd574cadf74ea34cc11c2bfdc9757be","tid":113159,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:37:51.000Z","msg":"唔係 一早已經比大陸買咗咩........<br />\n是但啦. .....無所謂. 唔會再關心. 有得睇就睇......無都算."},{"pid":"4fa105fe27fc936d4057d70ea706fc479e35df2a","tid":113159,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:43:21.000Z","msg":"日日唱紅歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\